{"tid":1700140,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"余德丞扮BTS泰亨冧暈鄭裕玲","createTime":"2019-11-08T10:36:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T08:48:41.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4c27793926a251f41917d6cd8fe1199634de3e8f","tid":1700140,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T10:36:25.000Z","msg":"眾所周知，鄭裕玲（嘟嘟）是韓國男團防彈少年團（BTS）成員泰亨的「忠粉」，昨日她出席活動時，獲余德丞送驚喜，染了灰藍髮色及戴有色隱形眼鏡扮泰亨，氹得嘟嘟開心不已！<br />\n鄭裕玲、陸永、C君、陳豪與余德丞昨日出席無綫節目《晚間看地球》記者會，眾人分別向嘟嘟送上「抗睡意」禮物，余德丞以BTS成員泰亨造型現身，除染灰藍髮色及戴有色隱形眼鏡，又跳舞派心心，冧到嘟嘟頻頻嗌「Good」及大笑，最後二人齊齊做心形手勢合照。<br />\n<br />\nC君：灰狼驚咗嘟姐<br />\n拍過無數購物節目的嘟嘟透露，今次搞搞新意思，介紹晚間旅遊好去處。陸永笑言最大挑戰是進入森林與灰狼玩，事前要上堂，導師叮囑要按指示做，否則會送命，嚇得他心驚驚，幸而最後有驚無險。C君則說：「入到去嘟姐完全唔驚啲灰狼，反而啲灰狼驚咗佢！」陸永即指觀眾看完節目後，不難發現嘟嘟能統治萬物。<br />\n至於早前舉家到泰國旅遊的陳豪表示，聖誕將再次外遊：「太太（陳茵媺）一早安排返加拿大，到時成家滑雪，好期待。（到時太太再晒水着相？）唔會啦！上次泰國泳裝相係我包辦嘅。（下次到你晒泳褲相？）捨己為人？好難，依家唔得，等我操弗身形先啦！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/VDth_Cf9sLk9nm3wsTrCew--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/dba5be5c58858b503caf194d547d8bd7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FVDth_Cf9sLk9nm3wsTrCew--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fdba5be5c58858b503caf194d547d8bd7&h=de07cdf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BD%99%E5%BE%B7%E4%B8%9E%E6%89%AEbts%E6%B3%B0%E4%BA%A8%E5%86%A7%E6%9A%88%E9%84%AD%E8%A3%95%E7%8E%B2-214500648.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BD%2599%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E4%25B8%259E%25E6%2589%25AEbts%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E4%25BA%25A8%25E5%2586%25A7%25E6%259A%2588%25E9%2584%25AD%25E8%25A3%2595%25E7%258E%25B2-214500648.html&d=zUJDlVqOtbKZlRnsKtUQBDyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=7d142703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BD%99%E5%BE%B7%E4%B8%9E%E6%89%AEbts%E6%B3%B0%E4%BA%A8%E5%86%A7%E6%9A%88%E9%84%AD%E8%A3%95%E7%8E%B2-214500648.html</a>"},{"pid":"8e9549df38ae0591719be35cb46ccf591c7daa58","tid":1700140,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T10:41:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media1.giphy.com/media/4Nx54rSLxs3vEsHaAy/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F4Nx54rSLxs3vEsHaAy%2Fgiphy.gif&h=5f65bdf9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a91535e98c820173fd44ea79c65a9efa04c891e3","tid":1700140,"uid":89660,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T10:43:58.000Z","msg":"Dodo可否不要老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"862f350b561758e6f03e9c45eb30ed550ba9313c","tid":1700140,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T10:51:07.000Z","msg":"令仔過咪華"},{"pid":"074c2b3fdee766c2565e8fdcaac475f6c6b2f5fc","tid":1700140,"uid":250865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T10:51:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e96ff1e6fe3dd731734515c371741e477cab2e8","tid":1700140,"uid":76632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T10:55:21.000Z","msg":"邊忽似V仔&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1fa60959f3e57f08600db53d5b417c3d043364","tid":1700140,"uid":165368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T10:55:46.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得V啡色靚仔啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67df79cd088774fc1e6a46000d58278fff1bafa","tid":1700140,"uid":181997,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T11:00:07.000Z","msg":"MM先係玩具反屌城見到，好撚醜樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g118V9j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg118V9j.png&h=714a4142&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4d27d9922e062443612a1d253fb2540dd1da0d4","tid":1700140,"uid":